Title: GUI Top
worldeditgui.commands.set.comment:
Perform the //set
Sets all the blocks in the region
worldeditgui.commands.copy.comment:
Copy the selection to the clipboard.
Perform the //copy
worldeditgui.commands.paste.comment:
Paste the clipboard’s contents
Perform the //past
worldeditgui.commands.move.comment:
Perform the //move
Move the contents of the selection.
worldeditgui.commands.rotate.comment:
Perform the //rotate
Rotate the contents of the clipboard.
Non-destructively rotate the contents of the clipboard.
Angles are provided in degrees and a positive angle will result in a clockwise rotation.
Multiple rotations can be stacked.
Interpolation is not performed so angles should be a multiple of 90 degrees.
worldeditgui.commands.rotate.xyz.comment:

worldeditgui.commands.stack.comment:
Perform the //stack
Repeat the contents of the selection.
worldeditgui.commands.flip.comment:
Perform the //Flip
Flip the contents of the clipboard across the origin.
worldeditgui.hotkey.open_config.comment: The key open the in-game config GUI
